author: The Irish Times
title: Coronavirus: Spain reaches 20,000 deaths after further 565 in 24 hours
description: Trump claims China has most deaths despite official statistics
content:
Spain has reached 20,000 deaths for the coronavirus pandemic and total infections increased to more than 190,000.
Spains health authorities reported 565 deaths in the last 24 hours. Only the United States and Italy have more deaths.
